sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_051_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Cancel Reservation
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Reservation feature profile

    CS->>CP: 1. ReserveNow.req
    Note left of CS: connectorId: <non-zero><br/>idTag: <Configured Valid IdTag><br/>reservationId: <unique id><br/>expiryDate: <future timestamp>
    Note left of CS: Validation: connectorId must not equal 0

    CP-->>CS: 2. ReserveNow.conf (status: Accepted)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Accepted

    CP->>CS: 3. StatusNotification.req (status: Reserved)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Reserved
    CS-->>CP: 4. StatusNotification.conf

    CS->>CP: 5. CancelReservation.req
    Note left of CS: reservationId: same as step 1
    Note left of CS: Validation: reservationId must match step 1

    CP-->>CS: 6. CancelReservation.conf (status: Accepted)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Accepted

    CP->>CS: 7. StatusNotification.req (status: Available)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Available
    CS-->>CP: 8. StatusNotification.conf
